- **Zeile 20** (gross stock-sale gains, [§ 20 Abs. 2 Nr. 1 EStG](https://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/estg/__20.html)): **{{ rule.outputs[1].value | money(currency="EUR") }}**
- **Zeile 23** (stock-sale losses, [§ 20 Abs. 2 Nr. 1 EStG](https://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/estg/__20.html)): **{{ rule.outputs[2].value | money(currency="EUR") }}**
